{"title":"闽山情思","authors":["朱碧森"],"dates":[{"year":1983,"month":12,"day":26}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"闽山情思"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朱碧森"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清流，一个现实的甜梦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清流，一个水灵灵的名字，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牵给我一幅湿润的春图。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有谁知，你曾是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个枯藤缠绕的梦？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当毛泽东沾着露水的脚步，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叩醒沉睡的小山沟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挥动的巨手如犁头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿破冻结的硬土，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在人们心里，开出一条沟渠。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于是，禁锢山野的土炮楼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连同几千年的污秽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被洪涛卷走；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山泉，也仿佛摆脱了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"卖身契的桎梏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢跃着，奔向江河，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"载着第一声欢呼……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"虽然，几十年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"波涛起伏，生死搏斗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"希望的原野上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总有清水长流。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宁化，一条弯曲的小路"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一折，立一面峭壁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一弯，垂一条深谷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白昼、黑夜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"包裹在浓雾之中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"方向、道路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"失落在密林深处，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唯有天上一线裂隙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给摸索者一张隐约的示意图。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哦，阳光、蒺藜交织的路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哦，星星、卵石铺就的路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光明与黑暗交接，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"希望与失望同途，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一段历史的经验"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"留给后来人，提醒前进的队伍。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁流，在这路上涌过，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战旗，从这路上飘出，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东指挥了一次"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胜利的进击，威震八闽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也是一回积极的防御，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了红色堡垒的巩固。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也许，革命多险阻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这路才如此弯曲；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也许，这路太曲折，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命才迂回反复——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个深沉的思想，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在大地上记录……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"归化，一个消逝的名字"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你选择这个名字，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是表达必然的归宿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还是自己的意志？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真的，在中国版图上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我再也找不到你。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你和你的业绩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飘然而去了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象太阳烤干的气体？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你和你的荣光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"暗淡失色了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象月夜隐去的云霓？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我不敢，有这样的怀疑！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你不再是一个行政区域，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新的地名并不会隔断历史。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田野上有绿柳、金浪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山巅上有青松、红旗……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你被一个伟人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"写进不朽的诗词，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"僻山野岭，才有"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世人注目，举国名气。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你又证明着他的伟绩丰功，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如同你的事业正在继续……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}